{"tid":2056801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢地盤天秤倒塌　有人受傷","createTime":"2020-06-09T02:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T03:45:13.000Z","uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1721d7d04b3c8717eabfe9a29dfa2e526dd872f7","tid":2056801,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢市武昌一建築地盤內的天秤，周二（9日）突然倒塌，砸中在建建築和附近的車輛，有人走避不及，被砸傷，現場一片狼藉。惟官方暫未通報事件，未知傷亡情況。<br />\n網傳影片顯示，地盤工人在場尋找是否有人被壓中；另有多輛途經地盤附近路面的車輛被壓中，石屎等雜物滿布路面，妨礙車輛通行。<br />\n交通廣播頻道隨後在網上發文稱，事發於上午約9時，在和平大道和秦園路路口附近的地盤內，天秤突然倒塌，現場有車受損和人員受傷，目前秦園路路口已經封閉，司機需繞路行駛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200609/photo/bkn-20200609103900657-0609_00952_001_01b.jpg?20200609105512\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200609%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200609103900657-0609_00952_001_01b.jpg%3F20200609105512&h=eff5e996&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39df06440946143851d9db20526eb4d5c7871f76","tid":2056801,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"恆指又升"},{"pid":"ca0693b7014332ed4c173a9298ef5c831ccfdb0e","tid":2056801,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0253b2e10733a42af10f2f4e80d2865a39b420ef","tid":2056801,"uid":36702,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗講   一定無人死   事主輕傷  <br />\n發現係美國佬做 <br />\n結果最後 中國 或會成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"6d3c2b1747dbdf435841b3a76e6b7938ea6a4954","tid":2056801,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"so good"},{"pid":"92fea27cc79ee9a279f03f4be036898501eef952","tid":2056801,"uid":62721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0253b2e10733a42af10f2f4e80d2865a39b420ef","tid":2056801,"uid":36702,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20